{"tid":2438463,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"2100 眾新聞 中國組 中國共產黨 中共建黨百年 黨史專家：共有91種革命精神｜ 武漢肺炎死者家屬去信北京","createTime":"2021-03-08T13:40:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T16:57:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"67a34d4b8a5ace9da0155452523df62040080ec8","tid":2438463,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T13:40:06.000Z","msg":"2100 眾新聞 中國組<br />\n中國共產黨 中共建黨百年 黨史專家：共有91種革命精神｜<br />\n武漢肺炎死者家屬去信北京 要求公開世衛專家組考察行程｜<br />\n內地工人維權討欠薪 反被屈過萬餐費<br />\n (眾新聞 中國組) 眾新聞中國組<br />\n20210308<br />\n逢星期一至五<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/iVY-s_s5zDQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FiVY-s_s5zDQ&d=5FApYPwYYRZ83iNn2U1Rv69osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=d8b6c842\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/iVY-s_s5zDQ</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n眾新聞<br />\n69.7K subscribers<br />\n<br />\n🔸中央黨史和文獻研究院梳理中共不同時期的革命精神，表示共計有91種，有政治學者形容有如文革爆發前豎立雷鋒精神。<br />\n<br />\n🔸新型肺炎死者家屬張海去信北京當局，申請公開世衛專家在中國考察時的具體行程。<br />\n<br />\n🔸7名討薪工人等侯與老闆會面期間在公司食堂用膳，簡單點了4個菜，卻被索價每人1萬元餐費。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com&d=5FApYPwYYRZ83iNn2U1Rv69osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=fd6e3276\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com</a>"},{"pid":"6a455731301e960157e2e08d0ba2aaeef7117dcb","tid":2438463,"uid":155095,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T13:44:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Eqdh-YuUUAIQ2_m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEqdh-YuUUAIQ2_m.jpg&h=352917c7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f2a1cf5d7f5a0df178d50786b7752342cccea7e7","tid":2438463,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T16:57:36.000Z","msg":"push"}]}